title: Mac OS 9 Companion Disk, International English
description:
Mac OS 9 Companion Disk
International English


This CD is in Mac OS extended format which
means it can't be read by Mac OS 8.1 and older systems.
It is primarily intended as a continuation to my
Mac OS 9.0.4 International English torrent.
The International English updates will not update any
North American English or British English systems.
If you're uncertain of what to do with a RAR-ed file, 
or an ISO image, please look at the description of my
Mac OS 9.0.4 International English torrent.
